# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  EXAMPLE — for testing the contact form locally with wrangler
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Cloudflare Pages Functions read environment variables from `.dev.vars`
# (NOT .env) when you run `wrangler pages dev`. Same key=value format.
#
# 1. Copy this file to `.dev.vars`
# 2. Fill in your real RESEND_API_KEY
# 3. Run:  npm run build && npx wrangler pages dev dist
# 4. Open http://localhost:8788/contact and test the form
#
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored — never commit real keys.

RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TO_EMAIL=chrisjasonmcqueen@icloud.com
FROM_EMAIL=onboarding@resend.dev
